{"type":"message","id":"3e347a0e","parentId":"ce0f0b69","timestamp":"2026-03-23T12:43:07.947Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_ab1ba06f99bb488ab0f37f17","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"embodied AI robot youtube video demonstration\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 10,\n  \"tookMs\": 6777,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0a57fc3506d2885f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nChina Showcases Robust Development Momentum of Embodied AI at Robot Conference - YouTube\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0a57fc3506d2885f\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yBnszGZlQZE\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"17ef4789d8f5f057\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe ongoing 2025 World Robot Conference in Beijing has seen the demonstration of robust development momentum by China&#x27;s embodied intelligence industry, with ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"17ef4789d8f5f057\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"August 12, 2025\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.youtube.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"03c28ad466abaa2c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAI Just Got a Body: Meet TienKung 3.0 | This Chinese Robot Can FEEL — And It’s Built for Factories! - YouTube\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"03c28ad466abaa2c\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3zLJrZIUNKI\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9f73e0a188c26f9f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAI isn’t just running in the cloud anymore — it’s stepping onto the factory floor.In this video, we’re diving into <strong>Embodied TienKung 3.0</strong>, the latest full-siz...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9f73e0a188c26f9f\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"1 month ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.youtube.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"551817fdad3e7683\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIntroducing: The NYU Center for Robotics and Embodied Intelligence - YouTube\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"551817fdad3e7683\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F4ZLdr_-OyA\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"19e403be9ea09df7\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nNYU Center for Robotics and Embodied Intelligence is a new group organized to advance research, education, and innovation at the intersection of AI and robot...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"19e403be9ea09df7\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"6 days ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.youtube.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"78eb7ded6f8c5b6f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWhat is Embodied AI? A Guide to AI in Robotics | Encord\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"78eb7ded6f8c5b6f\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://encord.com/blog/embodied-ai/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"db1f8564a6ce80ef\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThis is an example of robotics, relying on traditional control systems without the learning aspect of Embodied AI. On the other hand, ATLAS from Boston Dynamics learns to walk, run, and perform tasks by interacting with its environment and improving its skills through experience. This demonstrates Embodied AI, as the robot&#x27;s AI system adapts based on physical feedback.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"db1f8564a6ce80ef\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"January 15, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"encord.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"694ea5f0e6fb47ad\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGitHub - zchoi/Awesome-Embodied-Robotics-and-Agent: This is a curated list of \\\"Embodied AI or robot with Large Language Models\\\" research. Watch this repository for the latest updates! 🔥\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"694ea5f0e6fb47ad\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/zchoi/Awesome-Embodied-Robotics-and-Agent\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0c35b8407cafc542\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIQA: Visual Question Answering in Interactive Environments [CVPR 2018] [Github] [Demo video (YouTube)] Danie1 Gordon1 Aniruddha Kembhavi2 Mohammad Rastegari2,4 Joseph Redmon1 Dieter Fox1,3 Ali Farhadi1,2 1Paul G. Allen School of Computer Science, University of Washington 2Allen Institute for Artificial Intelligence 3Nvidia 4Xnor.ai\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0c35b8407cafc542\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"github.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e9c8d69a7c942592\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe rise of embodied AI: Robots that learn by doing - PAL Robotics\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e9c8d69a7c942592\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://pal-robotics.com/news/the-rise-of-embodied-ai-robots-that-learn-by-doing/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"60126f5e2aa34a62\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n<strong>This interactive demo represents a step forward in embodied AI, offering a glimpse into a future where humans and robots collaborate with seamless precision across distance and space</strong>.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"60126f5e2aa34a62\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"June 18, 2025\",\n      \"siteName\": \"pal-robotics.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fd04e074e11eeef6\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nEmbodied AI: What Is It and How to Build It?\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fd04e074e11eeef6\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/glossary/embodied-ai/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c0397821b0fc8ea7\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nNVIDIA Isaac™ Lab is an open-source, simulation-based modular framework for robot learning built on NVIDIA Isaac Sim™. Its modular capabilities with customizable environments, sensors, and training scenarios—along with techniques like reinforcement learning and imitation learning—let you teach any robot embodiment to learn from quick demonstrations.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c0397821b0fc8ea7\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.nvidia.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"11c3619f8d7a0fa6\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nVideo: First-ever live unscripted conversation between humanoid robots\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"11c3619f8d7a0fa6\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://interestingengineering.com/ai-robotics/humanoid-to-humanoid-ai-conversation\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"188a8f9c0df75b7b\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDuring the demonstration, Aria and David conducted their conversation across multiple languages, including English, Spanish, French, and German. Realbotix said this highlighted both the multilingual capabilities of its language models and the flexibility of its embodied AI platform. The exchange unfolded organically, with the robots taking their time to respond to each other’s statements rather than following a fixed conversational structure.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"188a8f9c0df75b7b\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"January 15, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"interestingengineering.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5979a3d5ea9ac8d5\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nEmbodied AI | Ai2\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5979a3d5ea9ac8d5\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://allenai.org/embodied-ai\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"cafb7e0df356d2ce\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nProjects like SPOC, PoliFormer, and FLaRe are leading the way—showing that simulation-trained robots can successfully operate in unfamiliar, real-world spaces. Explore SPOCPoliFormer: a masterful navigatorCheck out FLaRe · Our teams continue to push the boundaries of embodied AI, focusing on open data and platforms that support training and experimentation across the broader community.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"cafb7e0df356d2ce\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"allenai.org\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c3c6106629627a32\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nEmbodied AI | OpenDriveLab\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c3c6106629627a32\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://opendrivelab.com/EmbodiedAI\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ca22a55bd4225b60\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n2026.02.10EgoHumanoid: Unlocking In-the-Wild Loco-Manipulation with Robot-Free Egocentric DemonstrationThe first endorsement of human-to-humanoid transfer for whole-body locomanipulation. ... 2026.02.05Sparse Video Generation Propels Real-World Beyond-the-View Vision-Language Navigationwe investigate beyond-the-view navigation task in the real world by introducing video generation model in this field for the first time, pioneering such capability in challenging night scenarios.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ca22a55bd4225b60\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"opendrivelab.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"embodied AI robot youtube video demonstration","provider":"brave","count":10,"tookMs":6777,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"brave","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"0a57fc3506d2885f\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nChina Showcases Robust Development Momentum of Embodied AI at 