hat-learn-by-doing/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"60126f5e2aa34a62\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n<strong>This interactive demo represents a step forward in embodied AI, offering a glimpse into a future where humans and robots collaborate with seamless precision across distance and space</strong>.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"60126f5e2aa34a62\">>>","published":"June 18, 2025","siteName":"pal-robotics.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"fd04e074e11eeef6\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nEmbodied AI: What Is It and How to Build It?\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"fd04e074e11eeef6\">>>","url":"https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/glossary/embodied-ai/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c0397821b0fc8ea7\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nNVIDIA Isaac™ Lab is an open-source, simulation-based modular framework for robot learning built on NVIDIA Isaac Sim™. Its modular capabilities with customizable environments, sensors, and training scenarios—along with techniques like reinforcement learning and imitation learning—let you teach any robot embodiment to learn from quick demonstrations.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c0397821b0fc8ea7\">>>","siteName":"www.nvidia.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"11c3619f8d7a0fa6\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nVideo: First-ever live unscripted conversation between humanoid robots\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"11c3619f8d7a0fa6\">>>","url":"https://interestingengineering.com/ai-robotics/humanoid-to-humanoid-ai-conversation","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"188a8f9c0df75b7b\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDuring the demonstration, Aria and David conducted their conversation across multiple languages, including English, Spanish, French, and German. Realbotix said this highlighted both the multilingual capabilities of its language models and the flexibility of its embodied AI platform. The exchange unfolded organically, with the robots taking their time to respond to each other’s statements rather than following a fixed conversational structure.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"188a8f9c0df75b7b\">>>","published":"January 15, 2026","siteName":"interestingengineering.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5979a3d5ea9ac8d5\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nEmbodied AI | Ai2\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5979a3d5ea9ac8d5\">>>","url":"https://allenai.org/embodied-ai","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cafb7e0df356d2ce\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nProjects like SPOC, PoliFormer, and FLaRe are leading the way—showing that simulation-trained robots can successfully operate in unfamiliar, real-world spaces. Explore SPOCPoliFormer: a masterful navigatorCheck out FLaRe · Our teams continue to push the boundaries of embodied AI, focusing on open data and platforms that support training and experimentation across the broader community.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cafb7e0df356d2ce\">>>","siteName":"allenai.org"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c3c6106629627a32\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nEmbodied AI | OpenDriveLab\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c3c6106629627a32\">>>","url":"https://opendrivelab.com/EmbodiedAI","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"ca22a55bd4225b60\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n2026.02.10EgoHumanoid: Unlocking In-the-Wild Loco-Manipulation with Robot-Free Egocentric DemonstrationThe first endorsement of human-to-humanoid transfer for whole-body locomanipulation. ... 2026.02.05Sparse Video Generation Propels Real-World Beyond-the-View Vision-Language Navigationwe investigate beyond-the-view navigation task in the real world by introducing video generation model in this field for the first time, pioneering such capability in challenging night scenarios.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"ca22a55bd4225b60\">>>","siteName":"opendrivelab.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774269787942}}
{"type":"message","id":"7004fa93","parentId":"3e347a0e","timestamp":"2026-03-23T12:43:12.898Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"太好了！我找到了几个 YouTube 上的具身智能视频。让我给用户分享这些视频链接：\n\n[[reply_to_current]]\n\n小王子，我找到了几个 YouTube 上的具身智能 (Embodied AI) 视频，你可以看看：\n\n**🤖 机器人演示类：**\n\n1. **中国具身智能机器人展示** (2025 世界机器人大会)\n   https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yBnszGZlQZE\n\n2. **天工 3.0 - 有触觉的工厂机器人**\n   https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3zLJrZIUNKI\n   - 这个是满血版天工 3.0，能在工厂里工作，还有触觉感知！\n\n3. **NYU 机器人与具身智能中心介绍** (6 天前刚发布)\n   https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F4ZLdr_-OyA\n\n**🎬 特别推荐：**\n\n4. **史上首次 - 人形机器人之间的无脚本对话**\n   https://interestingengineering.com/ai-robotics/humanoid-to-humanoid-ai-conversation\n   - Aria 和 David 两个机器人用英语、西班牙语、法语、德语聊天，完全自然对话！\n\n你想先看哪个？我可以帮你找更多特定类型的视频，比如波士顿动力的 Atlas、特斯拉 Optimus、或者 Figure 01 之类的～"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":303,"cacheRead":17053,"cacheWrite":2896,"totalTokens":20258,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00008484000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000855}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774269787948}}
