{"type":"message","id":"f6bb5f94","parentId":"abb1f0e7","timestamp":"2026-03-23T12:44:45.160Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\n\n小王子，我试了连接 CDP (Chrome DevTools Protocol) 端口 9222，但是连接超时了 😅\n\n这说明你的浏览器目前没有开启 remote-debugging 模式。\n\n**要让我能控制你的浏览器，你需要：**\n\n1. **关闭所有 Chrome 浏览器窗口**\n2. **用这个命令重新启动 Chrome：**\n   ```bash\n   google-chrome --remote-debugging-port=9222 &\n   ```\n   或者 macOS：\n   ```bash\n   /Applications/Google\\ Chrome.app/Contents/MacOS/Google\\ Chrome --remote-debugging-port=9222 &\n   ```\n\n3. **然后我就可以：**\n   - 直接打开 YouTube 页面\n   - 帮你点击播放按钮\n   - 控制浏览器导航\n\n**不过要注意：**\n- 这样我会真的控制你的浏览器窗口\n- 视频还是会在你的屏幕上播放（我能控制，但你看不到我的\"眼睛\"😄）\n- 你需要在自己设备上看着浏览器\n\n要我帮你找一下 Chrome 的启动命令，还是你自己先启动带 remote-debugging 的 Chrome，然后我再来连接？🦊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":256,"cacheRead":24473,"cacheWrite":340,"totalTokens":25075,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00007168,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00007234}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774269880456}}
