{"type":"message","id":"74259d3a","parentId":"a7f015d2","timestamp":"2026-03-23T12:48:05.141Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在看到问题了！Chrome 需要 `--no-sandbox` 参数才能在这个 Linux 环境中运行（因为沙盒限制）。而且用户已经启动了一个 Chrome 进程带 9222 端口，但 agent-browser 无法连接到它。\n\n让我试试直接用 curl 或者检查 Chrome 是否真的在监听 9222 端口：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_dbe26528ceae4412b93cfabc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ss -tlnp | grep 9222 || netstat -tlnp 2>/dev/null | grep 9222 || echo \"9222 端口没有在监听\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":146,"cacheRead":28131,"cacheWrite":575,"totalTokens":28858,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00004088,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00004154}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774270082228}}
