{"type":"message","id":"66388484","parentId":"4a6c9e01","timestamp":"2026-03-23T12:50:39.857Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户还是希望我能直接打开浏览器播放视频。让我再想想有什么方法可以做到。\n\n问题是：\n1. Chrome 在用户的 pts/10 终端会话中运行\n2. agent-browser 无法连接到 9222 端口\n3. 可能是因为会话隔离或者网络命名空间隔离\n\n让我试试：\n1. 直接在那个 pts/10 会话中发送命令\n2. 或者用 process 工具向那个会话写入命令\n3. 或者试试其他方式\n\n首先让我看看有没有办法列出或连接到那个会话。我可以用 process 工具列出正在运行的会话，看看能不能找到 pts/10 对应的会话。\n\n或者，我可以尝试在后台启动一个新的 agent-browser 实例，带 --no-sandbox 参数。\n\n让我再试试直接用 agent-browser 带 --args 参数启动。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"小王子，我懂你想让我直接打开给你看！让我再试试其他方法～\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_5a9fce02d9dd47418b28b7cc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"agent-browser open \"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3zLJrZIUNKI\" --args \"--no-sandbox --disable-gpu --disable-dev-shm-usage\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":263,"cacheRead":29544,"cacheWrite":1786,"totalTokens":31599,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00007364,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000743}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774270232268}}
